reviewText: This is one of the most enjoyable dramas I've seen in quite a while.  The chemistry between the to leads was so nice. I would recommend this drama to everyone.

Always check the product comment to see if item is licensed. Otherwise, you might end up get DVD-R burned discs! Only trust licensed distributors like PMP or Poh Kim when buying. Purchase authorized copies and support the makers of Korean dramas.
Not my kind of story.  I didn't really get any "feels" from this drama but the shipping and communication from the seller was excellent.
Cute & funny story! Just loved it!!
